title: Batman Beyond Complete Series + Movie + (Dual Audio) MKV DVDRip
description:
Description
Encoded the entire series of Batman Beyond and The Movie into high quality MKV h.264 format.
The TV Series has English French, and Director Commentary audio with French and Spanish subtitles.
The Movie has English audio and Director Commentary audio with English and French Subtitles.
NOTE: All episode do not have dual audio, just the ones with audio commentaries or french audio, and all of Season 3.

Now you can enjoy this show in a great quality.

For playback all you need is the proper codec if you dont already have it.
Combined Community Codec Pack (which I prefer) or the K-Lite Codec pack should give you all you need and more to play these back.

You should be able to hear audio just fine if you have one of the mentioned codec packs above. If you cannot hear any audio and do not want to install a codec pack for some reason, then you do not have and need the nero aac audio codec
